	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1" facs="EHRI_DR-19430601_EN.jpg"/>
			<p>An informed source states on the basis of information assertedly just received from <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/719819/hungary.html">Hungary</placeName> that the <persName
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_pers-000202">Kallay</persName>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-948" type="subject">Government</term> has prepared and shortly will
				propose a special war <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1047" type="subject">levy</term> on <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-887" type="subject">Jewish property</term> along the lines of the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1047" type="subject">taxes</term> of that nature recently established in
					<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798549/romania.html">Rumania</placeName> and <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/732800/republic-of-bulgaria.html">Bulgaria</placeName>. [...] The source adds that <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-329" type="subject">anti-Semitic</term> members of <persName
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_pers-000202">Kallay’s</persName>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-948" type="subject">Government</term> declare <term
					ref="#ehri_dr_nationalities_hungarians">Hungarian</term>
				<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> should in their own interest practice
				more moderation and abandon their provocative attitude otherwise even severer measures will be applied to them in the near future.</p>
		</body>
